==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Locale
<hw>Lo`cale"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>local</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A place, spot, or
location.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A principle, practice, form of speech, or other
thing of local use, or limited to a locality.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>localisation</ent>⟦br⟧
